creator: Magic one games
descriptionHtml:
Welcome to Unscrew Jam Puzzle - a game that turns sorting screws into a colorful adventure!
Get ready for a thrilling adventure where screws, colors and sorting collide in a mesmerizing 3D world of challenges and fun. Every level brings a new challenge, making Unscrew Jam Puzzle a brain-teasing puzzle game that's hard to put down. Are you ready to dive into the Unscrew Jam Puzzle madness and emerge as the ultimate unscrew master? Let's find out!

Unscrew Jam Puzzle is suitable for all ages. Here is how to play:
- Tap to remove screws in correct order to get rid of all colorful boards
- Note that color boards are placed in layers, so plan your moves wisely
- Fill toolboxes with matching color screws to pass all levels
- Each toolbox contains 3 screws only
- Think carefully before making any moves because the waiting holes are limited and you cannot move back your screws
- Stuck in jam? Power up a booster to secure a victory with ease!

FEATURES:
- Easy to play but hard enough to train your brain
- Explore various board themes in unique shapes and colors
- Enjoy ASMR sounds for a relaxing experience
- Conquer 1000+ levels with tricky challenges
- Unlock amazing features and obstacles
- Earn fantastic rewards and dominate with boosters!

Ready to screw your way to victory? Get Unscrew Jam Puzzle now and experience the thrill of 3D sorting puzzle with endless challenges and fun!
